Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,BAN'S TRUTH
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can't fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's barely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even with my Kōmanotsue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it appears this spear\Nis all that stood between me and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost died trying to test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had a firm grasp\Nof your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you went above and beyond\Nmy expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you kill me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this body is the base of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The base... of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To be concise,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the man before us\Nboth is and is not Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the Secret Spell of Frozen Time\Nisn't a spell you can cast on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can't be successfully cast\Nwithout the highest levels of Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, because I wasn't\Nstrong enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not only was I was caught in the spell,\Nbut Hadorra was freed in about a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so my friends and I gathered again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I completed the Aban Style\NSword Technique and defeated Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the only one who could properly\Ncast the Secret Spell of Frozen Time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is none other than\NDark King Ban himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mystban never really existed\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obvious from what he just told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Myst is a powerful monster\Nof the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrusted with his master Ban's body,\Nor a copy of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he fused with it to create Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Any creature under the Secret Spell of\NFrozen time becomes an immovable statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there were a monster that could\Nmerge with that body and control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it would create a super warrior\Nwith an immortal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster with that power is Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the real Myst's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're correct, Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This body is King Ban's.\NKing Ban's original body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban entrusted me with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and ordered me to hide its identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, he allowed me\Nto use its power to fight when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I require\NKing Ban's permission to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the black Myst\Nthat covers King Ban's true face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill was defeated and I revealed your...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It matters not.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us admit what happened.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their power was greater\Nthan we anticipated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was almost killed by Dai.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems the time has come where I must\Ntake back what I have placed in your care.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My king. I shall return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The true body of Dark King Ban\Nthat is unrivaled in the Trio of Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to live a life\Nas close to eternal as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I divided my body into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This base body retains\Nmy wisdom and Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And my youth and strength\Nwent into this other body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With every full solar eclipse,\NI recast the Secret Spell of Frozen Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep my body sealed at its peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the bodies become one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How many millennia has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,THE ADVENT OF BAN,\NTHE TRUE DARK KING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will no longer be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku's Kōmanotsue\Nhas served its purpose well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had him make it for my protection.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For when I took on a weaker, elderly form.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that this body is whole,\NI have all that I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my complete power back so quickly.\NThings may take some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I may go a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like my hypothesis was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban has now regained his original body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were fighting against someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who you could consider to be\NDark King Ban himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing off when\Nit's not really your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a parasite\Nwho couldn't do anything on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just its voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand insults of that nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... That's your...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A gaseous life form?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's better to think of it\Nas a mass of Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was possessing Ban's body\Nwith that gaseous body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, it was covering his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but when fighting, it broke that seal\Nand entered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What this ghost thing did\Nto Popp and Grand Master...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no physical form,\Nso I am immune to all physical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge at me carelessly and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a mass of Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm something between a ghost\Nand a gaseous life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born from the dark thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of thousands of years\Nof battle in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With my instinct to fight on\Neven without a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually I was able to\Ncontrol other living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I capture a creature, its soul\Nis erased and then it becomes mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Underworld I moved from one strong\Ncreature to the next, growing in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you never lost respect\Nfor strong men like Hadorra and Baran,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was because you had no body of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While I can become strong\Nsimply by stealing the body of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot grow strong\Nthrough my own efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who could do that, I respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I envied them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me\Nwith such pity, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this accursed body,\NI was able to meet King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And King Ban told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was your destiny from birth\Nto serve me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban needed my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed a great master like King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I must continue to work for King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of Miss Maam!
