Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TIGER SHATTER FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}INCINERATING INFERNO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Not a bad body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam's body has been taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd suggest not holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if you are prepared\Nto attack one of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One cannot fight if afraid of losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be as strong as\Nwhen you used Ban's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what happens to her\Nif we can eliminate Master Dai's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You might hurt Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Myst! The same goes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hostage like that\Nisn't something befitting of you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm using this girl\Nas a shield, then you're gravely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This little girl's body, in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this really Maam?\NShe's strong! Too strong!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was warning you\Nwhen I told you not to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl normally suppresses her power\Nout of concern for her opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I use her power to the fullest\Nwithout hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate Maam will...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but with my Aura Knuckle,\NI can blow Myst away with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're finally serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your punch will pulverize Maam, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it will! That's how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but understand that\Nit's necessary for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no attack that can\Nconveniently defeat Myst alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! Air attacks!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even with an Air attack,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to leave Maam unharmed\Nand only defeat Myst is a difficult feat.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could move normally,\NI'd do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam is a Disciple of Aban.\NShe believes in the power of light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the legendary skills\Nof the Hero more than anyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I would put my faith in the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what it means\Nto learn from one's own student.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Aban Style Spear Technique,\NAir Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're counting on you, Sir Aban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it worked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before I hit, it left Maam's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It should still be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Where the hell did it go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Its next target...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was after you from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It went after the wounded\Nand immobile Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My Air Strike was reflected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel's body has begun emitting\Nincredibly powerful Dark Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what reflected\Nthat light attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, my friends!\NThis is why I chose Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I never cared about\Nthat little girl's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've reached this point
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter\Nif even his entire body is damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel any pain, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First it was Maam, now you plan\Nto use Hyunckel's body until it's ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This body is the last!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared it specifically\Nfor when I return King Ban's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the decision to make\Nthis body my own over a decade ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Aura! It rivals the Aura it exuded\Nwhen it fused with Ban's body!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness the birth of the new Dark Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Myst...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! Right now I'm moving\Nthrough your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear your inner voice well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul will vanish\Nand this body will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:17.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:28.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:45.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:49.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:55.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:23:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:23:02.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:09.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:14.93,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:20.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:26.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Myst was after Hyunckel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside Hyunckel's mind,\Nthe two clash many times.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Ban, the True Dark King\Nfinally reveals his true form.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai casts aside his doubts\Nand faces him with his strongest attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Dai land the first blow against Ban?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Demonic Guard of Heaven and Earth"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
